#: ../../configuration.rst:76 cf265016fa9c453f8dfd720fb84c9dc4
msgid "torrent_health"
msgstr "torrent_health"

#: ../../configuration.rst:77 aedbe15749b948bfbff1a128ee34c738
msgid ""
"Settings for the BitTorrent swarm health tracker (``poetry run torrent-"
"health``) and the CIRCL IP enrichment (``poetry run enrich-ips``). All "
"keys are optional; the defaults below apply when the section is missing."
msgstr ""
"Paramètres du tracker de santé des swarms BitTorrent (``poetry run "
"torrent-health``) et de l'enrichissement IP CIRCL (``poetry run enrich-"
"ips``). Toutes les clés sont optionnelles ; les valeurs par défaut ci-"
"dessous s'appliquent si la section est absente."

#: ../../configuration.rst:81 044f368f227c4cd0aa7431d36f67645c
msgid ""
"Retention keys (``*_days``) accept ``0`` to mean \"unlimited — never "
"expire\"."
msgstr ""
"Les clés de rétention (``*_days``) acceptent ``0`` pour « illimité — "
"jamais d'expiration »."

#: ../../configuration.rst:87 825096634de44d63b1a7d3f18ed70476
msgid "Key"
msgstr "Clé"

#: ../../configuration.rst:88 cb37baf78ec8434f8fdb5a93d2e6124d
msgid "Default"
msgstr "Défaut"

#: ../../configuration.rst:89 d443f98e0d1f4372a87aad1cccd72be4
msgid "Description"
msgstr "Description"

#: ../../configuration.rst:90 42c985658ecf480cb281b7902f447182
msgid "``scan_retention_days``"
msgstr "``scan_retention_days``"

#: ../../configuration.rst:91 2d8422d547854d63a1e04b34ac3a6611
msgid "``30``"
msgstr "``30``"

#: ../../configuration.rst:92 a0c13335124641f19054076eff1701d3
msgid ""
"How long each scan entry (with peer sample) is kept in Valkey. ``0`` "
"disables the TTL so the history grows unbounded."
msgstr ""
"Durée de conservation de chaque scan (avec son échantillon de peers) dans"
" Valkey. ``0`` désactive le TTL, l'historique croît sans limite."

#: ../../configuration.rst:94 05c312fb7dfb428c9d138f1de3e16d35
msgid "``dead_threshold_days``"
msgstr "``dead_threshold_days``"

#: ../../configuration.rst:95 023240996a9044c1be31d7c8a37467e4
msgid "``90``"
msgstr "``90``"

#: ../../configuration.rst:96 4fd0feed5630481da4238956a304ccca
msgid ""
"Metadata for an infohash with no peer seen for this many days is purged "
"at the end of every ``torrent-health`` run. ``0`` disables the purge."
msgstr ""
"Les métadonnées d'un infohash sans aucun peer observé depuis ce nombre de"
" jours sont purgées à la fin de chaque passe ``torrent-health``. ``0`` "
"désactive la purge."

#: ../../configuration.rst:99 b1e1f273176d4ce0a9df3a5466ca8005
msgid "``ip_cache_ttl_days``"
msgstr "``ip_cache_ttl_days``"

#: ../../configuration.rst:100 ../../configuration.rst:118
#: 08cd7a0593fd4cacad51e51dc2234183 12dda7eddffd4b04b2c8d9c11df7d4bf
msgid "``7``"
msgstr "``7``"

#: ../../configuration.rst:101 f61add03660b4bcab67f3d5667ea2e5e
msgid ""
"How long a CIRCL-enriched IP record (ASN / org / country / PTR) is "
"cached. ``0`` makes the cache permanent."
msgstr ""
"Durée de cache d'un enregistrement IP enrichi par CIRCL (ASN / org / pays"
" / PTR). ``0`` rend le cache permanent."

#: ../../configuration.rst:103 9c6f41ff863d4b78990f6aaf20484296
msgid "``scan_duration_seconds``"
msgstr "``scan_duration_seconds``"

#: ../../configuration.rst:104 3758ec78005649f9a51e541887b445ba
msgid "``45``"
msgstr "``45``"

#: ../../configuration.rst:105 8cafe5bcf0a5406abbc83783a23832df
msgid ""
"Seconds the scanner stays in each swarm before snapshotting peers. Raise "
"for very large swarms (many handshakes to complete)."
msgstr ""
"Nombre de secondes pendant lesquelles le scanner reste dans chaque swarm "
"avant l'instantané des peers. À augmenter pour les gros swarms (beaucoup "
"de handshakes à compléter)."

#: ../../configuration.rst:107 08ce4ede6eac40f8a3c5ef58181f919b
msgid "``batch_size``"
msgstr "``batch_size``"

#: ../../configuration.rst:108 5273ffd75abd490ab3bbf616b41dda3c
msgid "``10``"
msgstr "``10``"

#: ../../configuration.rst:109 23c3a94405894d908f4ccbaad075afdf
msgid "Number of magnets scanned concurrently within one session window."
msgstr "Nombre de magnets scannés en parallèle dans une fenêtre de session."

#: ../../configuration.rst:110 7ff72434dd86404eb1ec54f5329ee042
msgid "``alive_interval_hours``"
msgstr "``alive_interval_hours``"

#: ../../configuration.rst:111 99d43dbebfc545e08889823701786fcd
msgid "``6``"
msgstr "``6``"

#: ../../configuration.rst:112 3e96f935bae645ba95463a505ae248b8
msgid ""
"Adaptive schedule: minimum interval between scans for a swarm that had "
"peers on its last visit."
msgstr ""
"Ordonnancement adaptatif : intervalle minimum entre deux scans d'un swarm"
" qui avait des peers à sa dernière visite."

#: ../../configuration.rst:114 3d846e35d66344abb386b842799ffa3e
msgid "``dead_interval_hours``"
msgstr "``dead_interval_hours``"

#: ../../configuration.rst:115 17be2b07343d4a54b98fe01eb13287da
msgid "``24``"
msgstr "``24``"

#: ../../configuration.rst:116 55d076d6ea694593890cfd9bb6f956a4
msgid "Same, for swarms that had zero peers recently (< 7 days)."
msgstr "Idem, pour les swarms sans peer récemment (< 7 jours)."

#: ../../configuration.rst:117 c2313cdbd36c45958a705f62dd89c506
msgid "``frozen_interval_days``"
msgstr "``frozen_interval_days``"

#: ../../configuration.rst:119 7ba3c1edc803432aa0399ad259d2a722
msgid "Same, for swarms with no peer observed for more than a week."
msgstr "Idem, pour les swarms sans peer observé depuis plus d'une semaine."

